A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a treasure chest bursting open on a workbench, spilling out golden mechanical gears, intricate clockwork components, and shimmering tools. The chest sits in a craftsman's workshop with warm amber lighting, surrounded by scattered blueprints and technical diagrams. Jewel-toned gems shaped like abstract code symbols tumble out alongside the golden pieces. The scene has a nostalgic, sepia-toned warmth with rich ochre and bronze colors, cross-hatching textures, and the aesthetic of mid-century technical illustrations found in popular mechanics magazines.
